name: Macey Beanie
description:
The Macey Beanie is a fun beanie for winter! Made with a stitch that gives it just enough texture and a cute look. Every beanie is made to order. You pick your colors and let me know in your "notes to seller"




Care Instructions:
I always suggest hand wash, lay flat to dry since it's handmade.


**Due to yarn dye lots and differences in computer monitors, colors may vary slightly from the pictures.**

Pattern By Snappy Tots: http://www.snappy-tots.com/

name: Boot Cuff
description:
Boot cuffs are perfect for dressing up a pair of boots, and look great when worn with jeans, leggings, or skirts.

Easy to wear, just slip them on before your boots! Cuffs are about 6" long, they fit a calf size of about 15" (if you need a larger or smaller fit, please measure your calf at the widest point where they will be worn and include the measurement in your notes to seller when ordering).

Your cuffs will be made in the color you specify in the notes to seller when ordering. Buttons will be coordinated based on availability at my local craft store.
